Package: geodetect
Type: Package
Title: Deep Learning for Geospatial Object Detection
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-04-25
Authors@R: 
    person("Lalit", "BC", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = ("lalitiaas@gmail.com")
Description: Tools for deep learning-based object detection on geospatial raster data.
    Implements a Faster R-CNN model with a ResNet-50 and feature pyramid network
    backbone using the 'torch' package. Provides utilities for reading raster data,
    generating image tiles, preparing datasets from bounding-box annotations,
    training models, running inference on large rasters, and exporting predictions
    as 'sf' objects for spatial analysis.
